convert compiler directoves from SX-ACE sxf90/sxf03/sxc++/sxcc to SX Aurora TSUBASA directives
for nfort/ncc/nc++.

usage:
	sx_to_aurora.py <sourcefile> [...]

sourcefile will be backed to <sourcefile>.sxbkup, directives will be added.
Old directives remain in place, calling it several times will add new directives several times.
